7 AS INTRODUCED
8 An Act relating to professions and occupations;
enacting the Oklahoma Professions and Occupations Act
9 of 2026; providing for noncodification; and providing
an effective date.
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
14 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
15 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma
16 Professions and Occupations Act of 2026".
17 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
